To improve productivity, here are some tips:

1.  Set clear goals and priorities;
2.  Create a schedule and stick to it;
3.  Break down complex tasks into smaller ones;
4.  Minimize distractions (turn off notifications, find a quiet place to work);
5.,  Use the Pomodoro technique (work for 25 minutes, then take a 5-minute break);
6.  Take care of your physical and mental health (get enough sleep, exercise, eat right);
7.  Learn to say "no" to tasks that are not important or urgent.

